      • get

        @Nullable
Object get(String propertyName)
        Get the property value. propertyName will be a Action key like Action.NAME.

        Common property names are Action.NAME, Action.SHORT_DESCRIPTION, Action.CONFIRMATION, and Action.DISPLAY_CLASS.

        Parameters:
        propertyName - the property name.
        Returns:
        the value or null.
